"{\"uid\": \"thestar.com.my-news-world-2024-08-06-olympics--defending-champs-france-rally-past-germany-to-reach-olympic-men039s-volleyball-semis\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Tuesday, 06 Aug 2024  PARIS, Aug. 5 (Xinhua) -- Defending champions France rallied from two sets down to beat Germany 3-2 on Monday for the men's volleyball semifinals of the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 187, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 68, \"end\": 74, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9567194184183273, \"rank\": 0.03240286474999001, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 110, \"end\": 117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.903102607119627, \"rank\": 0.10728608783816306, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earvin Ngapeth scored 21 points and Trevor Clevenot added 20 as the French men landed the 18-25, 26-28, 25-20, 25-21 and 15-13 victory in the quarter-finals in one hour and 53 minutes.\", \"from\": 189, \"to\": 373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 257, \"end\": 263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.6638780030191265, \"rank\": 0.4629900376478366, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We were ready for a tiebreak.\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 405, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We expected it.\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why we did not panic after being down 2-0.\", \